data: The New Year festivities were over; in the hall of the old country Manor the guests had danced and sung, had stood hand in hand in a widening circle, listening to the clanging of bells in the church-tower near by.
Vaizey, George de Horne, Mrs., 1857-1917; Michael, A. C. (Arthur C.) [Illustrator]
